cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper presents a method for activity recognition using semi-supervised learning and convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) as CNNs are commonly used in image recognition tasks. The paper also involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) as it deals with recognizing human activities. Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it uses machine learning techniques to recognize activities. Finally, the paper involves neural networks (cs.NE) as it uses CNNs for feature learning.
